# BuzzTier Sales Engine – Pipedrive Config

## Pipeline
- Name: BuzzTier Sales Engine
- Default currency: USD (adjust as needed)

## Stages
1. New Lead — BuzzStore (probability: 10%)
2. Qualified by BuzzGPT (30%)
3. Trial / Free Tier Active (50%)
4. BuzzTier Pro Activated (80%)
5. Renewal / Expansion (90%)
6. Won / Active Subscriber (100%)
7. Lost / Churn (0%)

## Activity Types
- buzz_call
- buzz_sms
- buzz_email
- buzz_demo

Configure these in: Settings → Company → Activity types.
